Dear John,

I somewhat have the feeling that you felt attacked
when I made some comments (questions) after your
SIAM talk. In case I have offended you in any way,
I would like to apologize for that. I just wanted
to mention the work of Juettler, Wagner and myself
on rational motion design, since I got the impression
you are not aware of it. Unfortunately, I am sometimes
not able to say these things in an appropriate form
and afterwards I regret it a lot.

Hoping that you are not too upset, I remain

with best regards,

Helmut

