Helmut, 

I appreciate your note.  
I am undoubtedly too sensitive about comments after a talk, and 
interpret them as attacks rather than constructive help.
It is probably because of the passion that we all feel for our work,
and the wish to have it accepted and appreciated.
It was very good of you to get back to me about this.
I will be sure to look over your work on rational motion more carefully.
I have the highest respect for your work in geometric design.

